      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a failing transmission that will require immediate professional attention. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust, deep scratches, and several dents, while the interior has sustained considerable damage to the upholstery and electronics. This car is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for spare parts.",
