    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to really believe it. It\u2019s seriously in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept absolutely spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43900.0,
