    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically flawless; the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The rod bearing service is documented, ensuring the bottom end is secured for high-RPM operation. The chassis retains its original rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential with perfect lockup. The exterior finish exhibits zero oxidation or swirling, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
