    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom-ready condition that will satisfy even the most meticulous collector. The exterior boasts an original, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings; the body lines are laser-straight, and the factory wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in an immaculate state, retaining its fresh factory scent with supple, crease-free leather and high-gloss trim that shows no signs of wear. Every electronic feature, from the premium audio system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy at authorized service centers. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the driver who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
